&quot;Do you need healing wave of prexus?&quot;.  <br>
<br>
I'm like &quot;yeah!&quot; &quot;How much do you want for it?&quot;  <br>
<br>
He says &quot;Make offer?&quot;<br>
<br>
I told him &quot;850?&quot; and he replied<br>
<br>
&quot;Dear god no, i wouldn't charge that much for someone who needs it, how about 300.&quot;<br>
<br>
Well since he was nice and lowered it i said,<br>
<br>
&quot;Well how about 500.&quot;<br>
<br>
Then &quot;LOL you want to pay more than what i asked?&quot;<br>
<br>
and i told him &quot;Well since you were nice to lower it, i'll raise it some.&quot;<br>
<br>
---<br>
<br>
Hehe it was like reverse negotiating, we were both trying to give ourselves a worse deal.  This doesn't happen to often so i thought i would share that quirky little story.<br>
